{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f7018eefbf","title":"大字报——肃反错误是全国性的","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3e0be5e14d","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":6,"articleId":"f7018eefbf"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"1fe0ff6342","name":"中央音乐学院"},{"id":"7a37d92ca9","name":"徐荣坤"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ae0df134ba","type":"title","text":"大字报——肃反错误是全国性的","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f7018eefbf"},{"id":"730bf65b41","type":"authors","text":"中央音乐学院徐荣坤","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f7018eefbf"},{"id":"466604f1b6","type":"paragraph","text":"新华社天津6日讯　中央音乐学院学生出大字报比其他学校稍晚，但是来势很猛，几天内就贴出很多。主要的内容是：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f7018eefbf"},{"id":"628cabdbb8","type":"paragraph","text":"(一) 对党员干部进行人身攻击和谩骂，有的提出要开除某党员的党籍，有的把党员说成涂了漆的共产党员。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f7018eefbf"},{"id":"0c961706c5","type":"paragraph","text":"(二) 认为学校党委会有严重缺点，不满意和风细雨，质问为什么过去历次对待群众的运动都是暴风骤雨，而整党却要和风细雨？","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f7018eefbf"},{"id":"3fc4f3e3c3","type":"paragraph","text":"(三) 否定肃反工作的成绩，认为有几十个人被斗错了。徐荣坤在大字报中写着：肃反错误是全国性的，要求党中央再次实事求是地来重新估计肃反的成绩。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f7018eefbf"},{"id":"a733fed0e0","type":"paragraph","text":"(四) 对教学上存在的问题长期没有解决表示不满，认为学校大多数领导干部都不熟悉业务，不能领导学校。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f7018eefbf"},{"id":"963a5f2c8f","type":"paragraph","text":"(五) 一致要求把学校迁至北京。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f7018eefbf"},{"id":"af1ef94108","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：1957年6月7日新华通讯社编《内部参考》。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f7018eefbf"}],"page":{"id":"4efba6bab9","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f7018eefbf","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}